text:
Depending on your budget/deadline, you can either:
1 - order a custom stencil from the link above (might be more expensive, but this would be ideal) 
2 - you can follow this tutorial <https://learn.adafruit.com/smt-manufacturing/laser-cut-stencils|https://learn.adafruit.com/smt-manufacturing/laser-cut-stencils> to create a stencil layout for us, and purchase the raw material so that we can help you lasercut the stencil in a Nolop.


Bottom line is, we will need a stencil for your job to get a quality reflow soldering done.
